{"tid":1134073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幫港出聲silent majority 算唔算犯法","createTime":"2019-05-01T14:24:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T15:53:56.000Z","uid":204929,"like":69,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0da4245630db6af78f844b22dc248923d6a3b988","tid":1134073,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T14:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XvUKX2y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXvUKX2y.jpg&h=1357d5ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n犯罪或不誠實意圖而取用電腦<br />\n<br />\n根據第200章《刑事罪行條例》第161條，「有犯罪或不誠實意圖而取用電腦」，是刑事罪行。<br />\n第200章《刑事罪行條例》第161(1)條列明：<br />\n任何人取用電腦&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n意圖犯罪；<br />\n<br />\n有不誠實意圖而進行欺騙；<br />\n<br />\n目的是為了不誠實地使自己或他人獲益；或<br />\n<br />\n不誠實地意圖導致他人蒙受損失，<br />\n<br />\n無論是在他 / 她取用電腦時或在往後時間，有上述的意圖，都是違法。如果經公訴程序定罪，最高可被判入獄5年。<br />\n法庭會問兩個問題，去評定被告是否不誠實：(1) 一般合理和誠實的人，會否視被告的行為是不誠實？如果問題 (1) 的答案為「是」，就要問 (2) 被告是否知道自己的行為，會被其他人視為不誠實？如果問題 (2) 的答案同樣為「是」，在法律上，被告就會被認定是不誠實，無論被告認為自己的行為是否誠實，已無關重要。<br />\n獲益或損失不一定是經濟上的獲益或損失。第200章《刑事罪行條例》第161(2)條列明，「獲益」或「損失」不只是理解為金錢或其他財物的得益或損失，亦包括暫時性或永久性的獲益或損失。<br />\n<br />\n發布明知虛假的永久形式誹謗<br />\n任何人惡意發布他明知屬虛假的誹謗名譽的永久形式誹謗，可處監禁2年以及被判繳付法院判處的罰款。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢屈泛民派, 係有收錢(雖然佢自己on9， 畀人踢爆咗係自己打上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) <br />\n但係咁樣做, 會唔會另一啲人 我以為我哋係壞人? 為咗錢乜都做得出! <br />\n仲可能令人哋覺得我啲係非受賄賂， 但係明明我哋都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋嘅目的係為咗民主， 堅守信念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!"},{"pid":"31226e90a06d31427c13b0def091543a12b1114e","tid":1134073,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T14:26:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6dceea92cb98e797ff912d21f0120f587f699661","tid":1134073,"uid":191815,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T14:33:27.000Z","msg":"警察唔會受理<br />\n律政司唔會告<br />\n你放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c2844b7509f06eee774728867be8759a4ed7d5","tid":1134073,"uid":85586,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T14:34:12.000Z","msg":"講男姦女殺殺無赦嗰啲俾人告咗未<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7705d8aa82f95a7c4a826ab060384e702970cf0f","tid":1134073,"uid":204929,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"6dceea92cb98e797ff912d21f0120f587f699661","tid":1134073,"uid":191815,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T14:33:27.000Z","msg":"警察唔會受理<br />\n律政司唔會告<br />\n你放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T14:50:10.000Z","msg":"起碼引起公眾關注"},{"pid":"d6d310ebf392a210d9208e8097aea3dcd8f5a2df","tid":1134073,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:19:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6caed3a41317bc44873931d791fb33ff2b1e88b0","tid":1134073,"uid":69568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T10:16:12.000Z","msg":"你告咗先"},{"pid":"a1490dacd49137f727bfbc6aea76509cf691d947","tid":1134073,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T17:45:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b6d0603c1a5b255e4d8276d64cc75e3c4793dd5d","tid":1134073,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42c2844b7509f06eee774728867be8759a4ed7d5","tid":1134073,"uid":85586,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T14:34:12.000Z","msg":"講男姦女殺殺無赦嗰啲俾人告咗未<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T17:46:03.000Z","msg":"咁可以淨係同台灣引渡， 起碼嗰度法律公平啲"},{"pid":"3301db2a3a3a7a2fda9dd4d7f4c77157d35af080","tid":1134073,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:38:48.000Z","msg":"坐監啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 幫港出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef9092234998e264